---
// src/components/sections/AboutCTA.astro
---

<section class="cta-section-dark bg-tech-dark">
    <div class="bg-base"></div>
    <div class="tech-grid-bg"></div>
    <div class="ambient-glow"></div>

    <div class="container relative-z text-center">
        <h2>¿Listo para elevar tu estándar tecnológico?</h2>
        <p>Hablemos sobre cómo transformar tu gestión académica hoy mismo.</p>
        <a href="/contacto" class="btn-glow">Agendar Evaluación Técnica</a>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .cta-section-dark {
        padding: 10rem 0;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .cta-section-dark h2 {
        font-size: 3rem;
        color: white;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
    }

    .cta-section-dark p {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        color: #94a3b8;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
    }

    .btn-glow {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 1.2rem 2.5rem;
        background: var(--primary);
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 100px;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.4);
        transition: all 0.4s ease;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
    }

    .btn-glow:hover {
        transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.02);
        box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.6);
        background: #4338ca;
    }

    .relative-z {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 10;
    }
    .text-center {
        text-align: center;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .cta-section-dark {
            padding: 4rem 0;
        }
        .cta-section-dark h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }
    }
</style>
